---
title: Jerk Burgers with Citrus Slaw plus Roasted Potato Wedges & Spicy Jerk Mayo
description: Take a trip to the tropics with this fresh and bold jerk-seasoned burger with roasted potato wedges. Layered with hot and warm spices, our jerk sauce seasons the juicy burgers and flavors the dipping mayo—perfect for those potatoes! A crisp citrus-forward slaw tops the burgers, making every bite a perfect bite.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/670d73b1dc533226ca913b2a-3c82cf3a.jpeg
